overview: Sweating The Rent: Blonde Nikky is looking for a new apartment, and this one is close enough to her place that she heads over on her daily run to see it in the flesh. Shower Intruder: When Kristof Cale comes home to find the front door of his house open, he pulls out his camera and begins exploring the house to record the damage, but what he finds is sexy blonde Victoria Pure taking a shower! Good Clean Fun With Angella: When Angella shows up at the apartment she booked for her vacation after a long train trip, the last thing she wants to hear is "Come back tomorrow!" Creeping In For Rent: Blonde scammer Kyra Hot hasn't been paying her rent, so her landlord asks his friend Isiah Maxwell to help get what she owes. Party Girl Wants A Fucking Fiesta: Spanish hottie Lara Duro says she's in town for a "fiesta" with some friends, so when she can't afford the asking price on the apartment she booked.
title: Sex 4 Rent 16
